Miotastellar ( Miotabot X Stellarbot )

"Stellarbot", on almost every side of the body. have deadly weapons, shoulders, hands and feet all have sharp thorns. whoever and from any direction that would attack him, would be killed easily.

"miotabot" a change from bees, robots can be used to detect land mines. Because, this robot can smell trinitrotoluene or TNT from a distance of 100 kilometers. These two facts show that this robot is very careful and very sensitive to potential dangers.

The bee collects enemy armor And amazingly, wherever he lands, not a single enemy is damaged. Instead of destroying, this robot actually helps other robots heal.
